                "text": "I would recommend David Ribes' work on this subject of (other) domain logics. Lately I have approached visualization design studies as a method of soliciting (as Konrad has it) discussions with collaborators that are more about 'time correlations' and less about 'FOOBAR program suite'.\n(ribes 2019) "
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://dl.acm.org/doi/pdf/10.1145/3359140"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\n(otto 2024) "
